-low-cost-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echikoo%20trees%20can%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20to%2010-12%20metres%20tall%2C%20so%20leave%20at%20least%20four%20to%20five%20metres%20of%20clearance%20from%20walls%20or%20other%20large%20trees%20to%20avoid%20overcrowding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Prepare%20the%20soil%20by%20enriching%20and%20loosening%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparing%20your%20soil%20properly%20is%20an%20important%20step%20often%20overlooked.%20Chikoo%20prefers%20slightly%20acidic%20to%20neutral%20soil.%20If%20you%20are%20unsure%20about%20your%20soil%E2%80%99s%20pH%2C%20get%20a%20testing%20kit%20from%20your%20local%20garden%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDig%20a%20hole%20approximately%2045cm%20deep%20and%20twice%20as%20wide%20as%20the%20root%20ball%20or%20seed%20planting%20depth.%20Loosen%20the%20surrounding%20soil%20to%20encourage%20root%20expansion.%20Mix%20in%20a%20generous%20amount%20of%20well-rotted%20compost%20or%20farmyard%20manure%20to%20boost%20fertility%20and%20soil%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20organic%20matter%20provides%20nutrients%20and%20improves%20water%20retention%20and%20drainage%2C%20both%20critical%20for%20young%20chikoo%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T084610.605_11zon-1751426184.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chikoo%20prefers%20slightly%20acidic%20to%20neutral%20soil%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20it%20is%20prepared%20accordingly%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mahindra%20Nursery%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T084610.605_11zon-1751426184.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me