pensable%20as%20he%20designed%20and%20built%20a%20specialised%20machine%20to%20filter%20the%20millet%20milk%20effectively%2C%20producing%20a%20smooth%20and%20nutrient-rich%20base%20for%20the%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20process%20had%20to%20be%20invented%20from%20scratch%20as%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20market%20to%20filter%20millet%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20First%2C%20the%20naturally%20grown%20millets%20are%20sourced%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%20and%20farmer%20producer%20organisations.%20These%20grains%20are%20carefully%20washed%20and%20dried%20to%20remove%20dust.%20The%20cleaned%20millets%20are%20then%20milled%20and%20filtered%20to%20extract%20the%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20artificial%20flavours%3A%20Just%20real%20fruit%2C%20real%20grain%2C%20and%20real%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20millet%20milk%20is%20prepared%2C%20it%20is%20mixed%20with%20a%20natural%20stabiliser%2C%20developed%20in-house%2C%20and%20a%20modest%20amount%20of%20sugar%2C%20usually%20between%20five%20and%2012%20percent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruit%20used.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20steer%20clear%20of%20artificial%20colours%20or%20flavours.%20Every%20taste%20comes%20directly%20from%20real%20fruit%20pulp%20and%20nuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20millet%20ice%20cream%20is%20a%20meticulous%20and%20multi-step%20process.%20After%20mixing%20the%20millet%20milk%2C%20stabiliser%2C%20and%20sugar%20in%20a%20large%20tank%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20gently%20heated%20and%20boiled%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20is%20safe%20and%20properly%20combined.%20Next%2C%20it%20undergoes%20homogenisation%20to%20break%20down%20fat%20molecules%20for%20a%20creamy%20texture%2C%20followed%20by%20pasteurisation%20to%20kill%20any%20harmful%20bacteria.%20The%20mixture%20is%20then%20aged%20for%20approximately%20eight%20hours%2C%20which%20helps%20develop%20the%20right%20consistency%20and%20flavour.