%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deaths%20in%20Gaza%20rise%20significantly%20when%20a%20controversial%20group%20distributes%20aid%2C%20analysis%20reveals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751464440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-dandf-teaser-aid_6955653.jpg%3F20250702172834%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frise-in-gaza-deaths-linked-to-aid-distributions-by-controversial-group-13391481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sky%20News%20analysis%20shows%20that%20aid%20distributions%20by%20the%20Gaza%20Humanitarian%20Foundation%20(GHF)%20are%20associated%20with%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20deaths.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frise-in-gaza-deaths-linked-to-aid-distributions-by-controversial-group-13391481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Ancient%20Farming%20Method%20Turns%20Floods%20Into%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20tranquil%20rain-shadowed%20folds%20of%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Phek%20district%20lies%20Kikruma%20village.%20Here%2C%20the%20villagers%20practice%20a%20method%20of%20farming%20that%20has%20astounded%20agricultural%20enthusiasts%20for%20generations%3A%20Zabo%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20locally%20as%20the%20Ruza%20system%2C%20this%20ancient%20farming%20practice%20holds%20the%20secret%20not%20only%20to%20overcoming%20monsoon%20flooding%20but%20to%20fostering%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20with%20nature.%20The%20system%20was%20developed%20by%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Chakhesang%20tribe%20in%20Kikruma%20village.%20Evolved%20over%2080-100%20years%2C%20it%20ingeniously%20integrates%20farming%20and%20water%20management%20to%20conserve%20and%20use%20runoff%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20does%20this%20system%2C%20seemingly%20simple%20yet%20brilliantly%20executed%2C%20accomplish%20such%20feats%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20triple-tiered%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20Zabo%20refers%20specifically%20to%20a%20small%20pit%20within%20a%20paddy%20field%2C%20often%20used%20for%20fish%20rearing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Ruza%20denotes%20a%20much%20larger%20pond%2C%20typically%20around%20point%20two%20hectares%20in%20size%2C%20designed%20to%20store%20run-off%20water%20from%20the%20upper%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ruza%20system%20is%20a%20triad%20of%20thriving%20forestry%20at%20hilltops%2C%20productive%20agriculture%20in%20the%20mid-section%2C%20and%20flourishing%20paddy%20fields%20below.%20The%20upper%20tier%20protects%20village%20forestland%2C%20maintaining%20biodiversity%20and%20water%20catchment.%20In%20the%20middle%20tier%2C%20the%20ponds%20and%20cattle%20yards%20synergise%20to%20nurture%20the%20fields%20below%2C%20which%20not%20only%20yield%20rice%20but%20also%20support%20fish%20rearing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nutritious%20bonus%20that%20enriches%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(see%20figure)%20Schematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Schematic%20diagram%20of%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXe1ucv8b2-al_vOzVWweS-dSux--5KbTS28XhsegzN1cVAE96PxTRMxThM400yLOCfcv41azq35p0kDiFY2dP_NXGQXK1Ka8buAFJOdwstqVbP24rGc8Wnh_YS7Ws7Uvy6TZ4sV%3Fkey%3DJro5jQ19UXkFaRzOGjeFhw%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESchematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canr.msu.edu%2F%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.canr.msu.edu%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDelving%20into%20Zabo%3A%20The%20art%20of%20water%20management%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zabo%20system%20begins%20with%20capturing%20rainwater%20from%20hilltops%20and%20forests.%20This%20runoff%20is%20managed%20by%20gravity%20to%20flow%20through%20a%20carefully%20constructed%20network%20of%20small%20channels.%20These%20water%20channels%2C%20meandering%20through%20Kikruma%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20are%20meticulously%20designed%20to%20guide%20the%20rainwater%20into%20strategically%20placed%20ponds%20on%20terraced%20hillsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20any%20ponds%3B%20they%E2%80%99re%20reservoirs%20carefully%20crafted%20with%20rammed%20earth.%20These%20ponds%20are%20dug%20out%20at%20different%20levels%20on%20terraced%20hillsides%20and%20are%20strategically%20located%20near%20fields%20to%20ease%20the%20process%20of%20irrigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stored%20water%20is%20released%20slowly%20from%20the%20ponds%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20This%20gradual%20release%20controls%20water%20flow%20and%20prevents%20sudden%20surges%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446407%2Fscience-behind-why-northeast-india-receives-heavy-rainfall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20otherwise%20cause%20flooding%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20channels%20that%20supply%20the%20ponds%20have%20dual%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20they%20collect%20not%20only%20the%20precious%20rainwater%20but%20also%20nutrients%20from%20cattle%20yards.%20As%20the%20water%20passes%20through%20these%20yards%2C%20it%20picks%20up%20animal%20dung%20and%20urine%2C%20crafting%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20that%20fortifies%20the%20fertile%20paddy%20fields%20located%20at%20the%20hills%E2%80%99%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20ponds%20are%20also%20utilised%20for%20fish%20farming%2C%20providing%20an%20additional%20source%20of%20income%20and%20food%20for%20the%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C