ic%20farming.%20I%20would%20earn%20just%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20my%20organic%20produce%20in%20the%20conventional%20market.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%204%20lakh%20in%20just%20one%20season.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20doubled%20his%20income%20by%20selling%20organic%20mangoes%20through%20Sreshte%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20doubled%20his%20income%20by%20selling%20organic%20mangoes%20through%20Sreshte%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20selecting%20farmers%2C%20the%20couple%20carries%20out%20detailed%20research%20to%20verify%20that%20they%20adhere%20to%20the%20standards